  "response": "As of current scientific understanding and technology, it is not possible for humans or any object with mass to travel at the speed of light. According to Einstein\u2019s theory of relativity, as an object with mass accelerates closer to the speed of light, its mass effectively becomes infinite, requiring infinite energy to continue accelerating. Therefore, only massless particles, such as photons, can travel at the speed of light. Human space travel is limited to much lower velocities with existing technology.",
